included.summary:
Hello! 
As a recent graduate of the Ohio State University, I earned a Bachelor of Arts in New Media and Communication Technology and a minor in Visual Communication Design. 

Because I have a strong curiosity about user experience, I have a drive to always keep learning new findings and advancements within the field. I offer strategic web design and development skills, user experience research and interaction design knowledge. I am passionate about delivering web, mobile, and application experiences that are relevant, elegant, and intuitive. I am driven by the belief that good user experience design enhances the quality of life.

One of my passions is typography and custom hand lettering. View my work below, under "Organizations," under "Typography."

During my time as a student-athlete on The Ohio State Women's Team, I was part of the team that won the first ever NCAA Champion of any women's sport in Ohio State history. I am a two time Big 10 Conference Champion and two time NCAA National Champion.
